description_clean:
[AWS] ขอเพิ่ม policy ใน Iam role AWS
IAM User information(AD User): KHANINSI@scg.com
Policy information: AWS-CHEM-DIGITALTECH-POOL-DEV
The error suggests that you would we need to add aws-marketplace:ViewSubscriptions & aws-marketplace:Subscribe permissions in your IAM role to access the Models. Please refer below documentation for more details - [+] Simplified model access in Amazon Bedrock - https://aws.amazon.com/blogs/security/simplified-amazon-bedrock-model-access/#:~:text=Considerations%20for%20Anthropic%20models You can add inline policy like this on your role:
{
"Version": "2012-10-17",
"Statement": [
{
"Sid": "VisualEditor0",
"Effect": "Allow",
"Action": [
"aws-marketplace:ViewSubscriptions",
"aws-marketplace:Subscribe"
],
"Resource": "*"
}
]
}
Attach File
- RITM_ID.png

